  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But at this moment, he was completely different change.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You-- I show you the way in town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Maybe you can escape in this and this way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But the one, he said, but we have dresses from the Stuttgart-- from the-- then what we have.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was summer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I had my underwear shirt and my-- this shirt, I gave to this one and Sigmund gave to this young boy this-- later I knew-- he told me that his-- he could talk a little few words German.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Pascal-- he told us that he was a Jew from France-- from France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And Sigmund said-- he was-- he said, I take-- I take you home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I give you more dresses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he took him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the two other prisoners, they were still staying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But he show them the way how they could leave the shed without any danger for them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next day in the theater, I met Sigmund and I asked what happened about-- don't ask too [? more. ?] It's better if you know less-- better for you.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wanted to know what happened with Pascal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he make me [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's wonderful guy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, Then?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I feel that he had something with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was all because later, we-- our performances-- the gypsy was no more over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The next one was [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was-- he didn't play at this operetta, Sigmund.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my contact with-- was less and less with Sigmund.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I didn't received no news from Sigmund, one day during the [GERMAN] operetta, I have seen a part of newspaper.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
